	 to change delivery methods. Orders in violation of our policies will be c
	anceled without notice.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. Arrive earl
	y. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety Each accessible seat house
	s an armless freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairments and 
	their companions. The freestanding chair can be removed to accommodate a w
	heelchair.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/les-miserables-touring-seattle-
